Sasol to Pay $16 Million Penalty in Amended Competition Agency Settlement

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-02-28T10:01:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/sasol-to-pay-16-million-penalty-in-amended-competition-agency-settlement.html
  Sasol Ltd . agreed to pay a penalty
of 111.6 million rand to settle a competition investigation in  South Africa , the country’s competition agency said.  South Africa’s Competition Tribunal confirmed the amended
settlement agreement, it said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
